data.description: Don't miss your chance to own a great home in the highly sought-after Defoors Farm swim/tennis community! This Home has 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom with BONUS ROOM and features a front porch, bright and spacious entrance foyer, formal living room with coffered ceilings and upgraded light fixtures throughout the home. Open-concept on the main level connects the dining room, kitchen and family room. The kitchen features granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, eat-in dining area, and view to the family room with a fireplace. Enjoy the oversized owners suite with a sitting room and vaulted ceiling. The ensuite bathroom features a double vanity, large garden tub, separate shower, and walk-in closet. Enjoy the large covered patio overlooking the backyard. Amenities in the community include a playground, dog park, clubhouse, pool, and tennis courts.
